result.text: Attention all #dinosaur lovers! The Yanji Dinosaur Kingdom is waiting for you! This family-friendly destination is not only fun, but also #educational, making it the perfect place for a day out with the #kids. Get up close and personal with real dinosaur fossils and learn all about these incredible creatures that once roamed the earth. And when you're done exploring the exhibits, there are plenty of amusement rides to enjoy, including #rollercoasters that are sure to thrill visitors of all ages.
